XSLT translation Rules Test Cases


1. Input src files

*.f90

2. xevolver dir

*.f90.xev.d

3. src file translation

*.f90
-> src2xml -> *.f90.xev.d/src2xml/*.xml -> dir2xml -> *.f90.xev.d/dir2xml/*.xml

4. xsl translatoin and unparse to src file

input xml file: *.f90.xev.d/dir2xml/*.xml
current directory: *.f90.xev.d/test-(test rule name)

{input xml file} + {test-(test rule name).xsl} -> test-(test rule name).xev.xsl 
test-(test rule name).xev.xsl  -> test-(test rule name).xev.f90


for test use

5. expected src code

test-(test rule name).target.f90 -> (src2xml) -> test-(test rule name).target..xml -> (xml2src) -> test-(test rule name).target-xml2src.f90

6. comparing translation result with expected src

diff  test-(test rule name).xev.f90 test-(test rule name).target-xml2src.f90 > test-(test rule name).diff.f90



 